<h1 class="rm-manual">How the Wall Fell</h1>
<dl class="rm-manual"> <dt class="rm-manual">By</dt> <dd> <a href="file:///author/bernd-gehrke"> Bernd Gehrke </a> </dd> </dl>
<p>The Berlin Wall's fall sparked dreams of a radically democratic East Germany. Unemployment and privatization followed instead.</p>
